column11: Hi,thanks for your interest in joining us! Here are some things to note coming for our training sessions: 1. Session slots are on a first-come-first-serve basis. Please refrain from pulling out the last minute. Repeated cancellations will affect your chances for the subsequent trainings. 2. You must be fully vaccinated in order to participate in the training sessions. Please ensure that your TraceTogether application reflects that you are fully vaccinated. 3. Please be in proper attire prior to the session and be punctual! 4. Mask should be worn at all times,except during strenuous activities.5. Please maintain a distance of 2m from others in the USC. As we have training capacity limits,we will release the final confirmed attendance list on our telegram group. You may only join the training if your name is included in the final list. Join our telegram channel at bit.ly/NUSfloorballrecre for more updates. We hope you'll have as much fun as we do & see you at trainings :-)
